      <title>交易员称英国评估早期数据发布将刺激波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uk-reviews-pre-market-data-releases-traders-say-spur-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国正在重新审视其发布关键经济统计数据的时间，因为人们担心当前的交易前发布可能会刺激利率和债券市场的波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uk-reviews-pre-market-data-releases-traders-say-spur-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
